<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Seatplan Generator">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="">
                <span class="font-bold">Effective Date:</span> 09.03.2025
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            Welcome to <span class="font-bold">Seatplan.xyz</span>! This Privacy Policy explains how we
            handle your information when you use our seat plan generator. We
            value your privacy and aim to be transparent about how data is
            managed.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
            2. Data Collection & Storage
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            We do not collect, store, or process any personal data on our
            servers. All seat plan data is stored locally on your device using
            your browser's local storage. This means:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>
                No data is transmitted to our servers.
            </li>
            <li>
                Your seat arrangements remain private and accessible only on
                your device.
            </li>
            <li>
                Clearing your browser's local storage will remove all saved
                data.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
            3. Cookies & Tracking
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            We do not use cookies or tracking technologies to store personal
            data. However, we may use third-party services (such as analytics
            providers) to monitor site usage and improve functionality.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
            4. Third-Party Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            Our website may use third-party services (e.g., analytics or ads).
            These services may collect anonymized data according to their
            privacy policies. We recommend reviewing their respective policies
            for more details.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
            5. Security & User Control
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            Since all data remains on your device, you have full control over
            it. To remove stored seat plans, you can:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Clear your browserâ€™s local storage manually.</li>
            <li>Use your browser settings to remove site data.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
            6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be
            reflected on this page with an updated effective date.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact
            us at <a href="mailto:support@seatplan.xyz" class="font-bold hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors">support@seatplan.xyz</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</Layout>
